scene.message:
Masked Girl: Like this, I'm{nl}
painting your futures over{nl}
in black.{waitkey}{clearbox}Do you know why?{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Why do you get in my way?{wait_fr:30}{nl}
How can you bear the pain?{waitkey}{clearbox}You all might have{nl}
each other, Ms. Saeko,{nl}
families...{wait_fr:30} people to lean on.{waitkey}{clearbox}But I was always alone,{nl}
only able to watch everyone{nl}
look so happy together.{waitkey}{ret}

Masked Girl: As if any of you{nl}
could ever understand how{nl}
I feel!!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll destroy it...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
I'll destroy this school!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Look at that painting.{waitkey}{nl}
Pitch black and...{nl}
somehow really creepy.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Look at that painting.{waitkey}{nl}
Pitch black and...{nl}
somehow really creepy.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That can't be.{nl}
Sonomura should be{nl}
outside the school.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Maki's got some{nl}
serious style, wearing{nl}
a mask like that so boldly...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Don't you kids{nl}
get art?{waitkey}{clearbox}Isn't it a maaarvelous{nl}
piece of work?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It could be a trap{nl}
set by the Queen.{nl}
Be careful!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: There's no way Maki{nl}
would be here.{nl}
A Demon, perhaps...?{waitkey}{ret}
